name: Recharging... - Eye Mask
description:
Express who you are when sleeping with this "Recharging..." embroidered eye mask with an elastic band and high quality soft fuzzy fabric backing.  This eye mask is made with comfort in mind.  Give as a gift or keep for yourself!
All eye masks are made with Double Fold Bias Tape for the highest of quality and comfort.
All masks are cut by hand so each has its own uniqueness and feel!
Elastic band is securely attached at both sides. 
Eye mask is approximately 7 1/2" x 4". One size fits all.
Thank You for viewing our mask!
